	  <p>If you want to hide advertising banners from non members - do this...</p>
<p>Edit</p>
<p><strong>/inc/banners.inc.php</strong></p>
<p>Search for</p>
<pre>return $out;</pre>
<p>Replace it with</p>
<pre>if (islogged()){<br />&nbsp;&nbsp; return $out;<span style="white-space: pre;"> <br /></span>}</pre>
<p>Thats it!</p>
